narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Students gained an overarching understanding of European Politics and are also allowed to gain a deeper understand of the European countries of their choice.
It was great taking this class after taking the European Union. European Politics offered a broader overview of large issues facing Europe, with an emphasis on current events.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The class is great. Professor Cameron is great at managing discussions. No complaints!

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would recommend this course to anyone at Yale. Professor Cameron is a wonderful professor, and the course itself is interesting and engaging.
Take this class! Professor Cameron is great. He is incredibly knowledgeable and really cares about the material as well as his students.

I'd absolutely recommend taking European Politics with Cameron. The workload is reasonable, the topic is interesting, and Cameron is just a lovely guy and incredibly knowledgeable. I want him to be my grandpa.
